obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `^1[3. Allocation of seats in the House of the People.The allocation of seats to the States in the`
  line `House of the People and the number of seats, if any, to be reserved for the Scheduled Castes and for`
  line `the Scheduled Tribes of each State shall be as shown in the First Schedule.]`
